{"type": "article", "id": 13105, "title": "极简主义茶杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-06T06:49:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000210dQGEuIjXmtSp6kHb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自台湾设计师 Chun-Tso Liu 的一套作品，他试图打破传统的茶具繁琐的设计和华丽的外表，剥落不必要的元素，推出了这套极简的圆柱形茶具，他甚至让把手消失，只留下一小块凸起作为辅助手持茶杯的工具，或是茶包的固定。设计师 Chun-Tso Liu 工程师出身，后转型工业设计，一直专注于极简的设计，这是他的<a href=\"http://www.chuntso.com/\" target=\"_blank\">个人主页</a>，点击查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140730IDJ1sQZ0uEPd7YMT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6775\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140730iAMTpxv5RHoGsYuz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140731rOFx7GzkciuSqaAU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140731ivC1zM9S0yWcxVZb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}